\u0080\\u0099s team\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic competition\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhengdong cemented his legacy as one of the greatest table tennis players in Olympic history after winning the singles competition, joining fellow Chinese greats like Ma Long, Zhang Like and Wang Hao to win multiple medals.\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9936080877628125, \"rank\": 0.0028034936606489507, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ma Long\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13382519\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ma_Long\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Zhengdong\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1238}, {\"ngram\": \"his legacy\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest table tennis players\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"the singles competition\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"Wang Hao\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple medals\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s artistic gymnastics, China\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s Liu Yang won the gold in the rings competition, with fellow countryman You Jingyuan winning silver.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1496, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emperor_Ming_of_Han\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.534571450968369e-20, \"text\": \"Liu Yang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://db